# Creating Instance Pool in OCI 

# If you want to associate the instance pool with a load balancer or network load balancer, you need a load balancer or network load balancer and backend set.

# An instance configuration. An instance configuration is a template that defines the settings to use when creating instances.

# Pre-requisites
#    Appropriate IAM permissions to create and manage instance pools
#    subnet ocid
#    instance_configuration_ocid (a)

